  "detailed_description": "Super Antonio is a <strong>difficult 3D platformer</strong> with <strong>satisfying movement</strong>. Climb to the top while enduring a <strong>punishing experience</strong>.<br><br><strong>Controller is recommended!</strong> Xbox is fully supported. Playstation and Switch Pro Controller can be used with steam input (Gamepad Layout). <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118730/extras/68591c7cc070b0ce13eebb03c0c23946.poster.avif?t=1723779896\" width=406 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118730/extras/68591c7cc070b0ce13eebb03c0c23946.webm?t=1723779896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118730/extras/68591c7cc070b0ce13eebb03c0c23946.mp4?t=1723779896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Between <strong>4-12 hours of gameplay</strong>, depending on skill and difficulty setting.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118730/extras/8f4295cb088776d85d0aac0e132f76a8.poster.avif?t=1723779896\" width=406 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118730/extras/8f4295cb088776d85d0aac0e132f76a8.webm?t=1723779896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118730/extras/8f4295cb088776d85d0aac0e132f76a8.mp4?t=1723779896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Three</strong> difficulty settings:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Intended</strong> - There are no checkpoints - A frustrating experience for those with strong mental fortitude.<br></li><li><strong>Hard</strong> - Checkpoints will be set after fully completing a level - For those who do not wish to lose too much progress.<br></li><li><strong>Easy</strong> - Set your own checkpoints - For those who want a casual 3d platforming experience.</li></ul>",
